&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;0-2 years of accounting and reporting experience, with SEC reporting experience preferred Strong knowledge of US GAAP and SEC reporting requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;

