&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an Associate Vice President (AVP) of Paid Search to lead strategy, performance, and growth across a portfolio of Higher Education clients. This role is responsible for setting the vision for Paid Search within the vertical, scaling best-in-class performance frameworks, and driving measurable business outcomes across complex, multi-account portfolios.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role serves as a senior strategic partner to both clients and internal stakeholders. You will elevate our approach to enrollment marketing through data-driven decisioning, advanced platform capabilities, and deep vertical expertise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thought Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and evolve Paid Search strategy for Higher Education clients, aligned to enrollment cycles, program mix, and institutional goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate industry trends (e.g., seasonality, program demand, attribution challenges) into scalable, actionable frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish POVs on bidding strategies, funnel optimization, and audience targeting specific to EDU&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Strategy &amp;amp; Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
