&lt;li&gt;Oversee performance across portfolio, ensuring delivery against KPIs such as CPL, enrollment volume, and efficiency targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and unlock growth opportunities including new channels, budget expansion, and testing roadmaps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead QBRs and executive presentations with a focus on business outcomes and forward-looking strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
