&lt;li&gt;Implement standardized frameworks for testing, reporting, and performance analysis across accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with analytics to refine attribution approaches and measurement strategies, particularly for long consideration cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive consistency and rigor in how insights are translated into action and client impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
